00:00:00,075 --> 00:00:00,863
In the first scene

2
00:00:01,312 --> 00:00:07,875
we will explore what Docker is and why it is a revolutionary tool in the software development process

3
00:00:08,262 --> 00:00:15,012
Docker is a platform that uses OS-level virtualization to deliver software in packages called containers

4
00:00:15,412 --> 00:00:17,188
These containers are lightweight

5
00:00:17,613 --> 00:00:22,300
executable software components that include everything needed to run an application

6
00:00:22,700 --> 00:00:25,438
ensuring consistency across various environments

7
00:00:25,837 --> 00:00:29,413
This concept simplifies software distribution and deployment

8
00:00:29,925 --> 00:00:35,487
allowing developers to focus on building applications rather than dealing with infrastructure complexities

